{"tid":1405002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊公然將香港人昆蟲化 與納粹對付猶太人手法無異","createTime":"2019-08-04T07:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:10:40.000Z","uid":183758,"like":352,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"a74181ad4805896c5c38f336e07bacdd1d234400","tid":1405002,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:12:52.000Z","msg":"反猶太主義就是除蝨。除蝨非關意識形態。重點是要保持乾淨。 同樣地，對於我們來講，反猶太主義也無關意識型態，關鍵是在保持清潔，而這正是此刻我們會立刻著手進行的。我們即將要來除蝨了。我們只剩下兩萬隻蝨子，重點是要讓他們在德國全境絕跡。&mdash;&mdash;海因里希．希姆萊（Heinrich Himmler），1943 年 4 月。<br />\n<br />\n警隊公然將香港人昆蟲化 與納粹對付猶太人手法無異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d35166cf50b37a72d40d340570e56203b28bb6","tid":1405002,"uid":197989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c428374ebe84a4e8f4ad0e80528527b6e101c5ef","tid":1405002,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfeec7a4b502dc8ffb17be488c6c9f88974bfd2","tid":1405002,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"wtf"},{"pid":"ba6ea133774c33847ac65e3401a6cce3ab548b3a","tid":1405002,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:20:49.000Z","msg":"猶差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5e29007669497fffb083d16b5705e0ce26348b","tid":1405002,"uid":218,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:29:33.000Z","msg":"據赫斯說，首次用齊克隆B（藍色的<span style=\"color: red;\">氰化物</span>）來對付猶太人，儘管那些猶太人以為只是<span style=\"color: red;\">去除蝨子</span>，但很多人都懷疑他們將被殺死。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%BB%85%E7%B5%9